    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>black rice</strong> to a pot of plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook over a high heat for 30 min or until it's tender (it will still have a slight bite to it when cooked)</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, drain and set aside</p>",
