    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the<strong> cucumber</strong> into discs</p>\r\n<p>Slice each individual <strong>cucumber disc</strong>&nbsp;into<strong> matchsticks&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
