    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>red</strong>&nbsp;<strong>chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop ﬁnely</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
