          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>soy sauce</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;the juice of the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span><strong> vegetable oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and half the<strong> chopped chilli</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) &ndash; this is your <strong>chilli-lime dressing&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1413.-step-4-x200.jpg",
