          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> rice</strong> is done, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over the<strong> highest heat</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once your pan is <strong>very hot</strong>, add the <strong>beef strips</strong> with the remaining <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 1 min exactly, making sure you don&rsquo;t overcook them</p>\r\n<p>Once done, transfer them to a plate</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
