          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Season the <strong>beef strips</strong>&nbsp;with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and leave to rest for 1-2 min</p>\r\n<p>Wash the<strong> baby spinach</strong> and pat it dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
